@dd @BACKUP @DISK

- converts and copies files
- backup boot sector
- fixed amount of random data

# Backup or Clone an entire HD to another HD connected on the same system
dd if=<source> of=<target> [Options]

dd if=/dev/sda of=/dev/sdb

# Backup or copy disk partition
dd if=/dev/sda1 of=/root/sda1.img

# Restoring this image file to other machine after copying the .img
dd if=/root/sda1.img of=/dev/sdb3

